Package: heraldrules
Type: Package
Title: Regulatory Validation Rule Catalog for 'herald'
Version: 2026.2.3
Authors@R: person("Vignesh", "Thanikachalam",
                  email = "vthanik@users.noreply.github.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Compiled rule catalog that the 'herald' R package consumes to
    validate clinical-trial datasets against FDA, PMDA, and CDISC
    regulatory expectations. Ships CDISC CORE, FDA Validator, FDA
    Business, PMDA Validation, and NCI-EVS Controlled Terminology
    rules as pre-compiled gzipped JSON, plus herald-specific gap-fill
    and Define-XML spec checks. Rule authoring happens upstream in the
    herald-rules GitHub repository; only the compiled artifacts ship.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/vthanik/heraldrules
BugReports: https://github.com/vthanik/heraldrules/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    tools
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Config/testthat/edition: 3
